column2: SELECT Bucket, Minimum+(width*(Bucket-#)) AS Lower,   Minimum+(width*(Bucket)) AS Upper, COUNT(*) AS Count FROM ( SELECT  htmid,   # AS Minimum,  (# - #) / # AS Width,  CAST((# - #) / # AS INT) + # as Bucket FROM SpecObj WHERE class = &&& AND zWarning = # and survey = &&&  AND (z >= # AND z <= #)) a GROUP BY Bucket, Minimum, Width ORDER BY Bucket
